Package GameStates

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EditState  
    GameState
    GameState is the abstract class in this package all the methods described below are inhereted in the other classes in this package
    gStateMan
    the gStateMan class is used to switch between gamestates.
    HighscoreState
    the highscore state is switched on when you are done playing or when you die, when you switch to this state the higscore menu is drawn.
    MenuState
    the menustate is the fist state in the game and is state you constantly return when you want switch from playing the game and editing levels.
    PlayState
    in the playstate we set up the game in this class the actual maze runner is created.
